      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STRIKE IT MIKE (1) was well backed last start but ran below expectations when fifth (30.97), beaten 10 lengths. Was in the money the start prior. Can make amends. DR. AXEL (2) jumped from a low draw and boxed on well to finish third last time, beaten 2 lengths (24.61) behind Turtle Time at this track. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to his name from five starts. Will give a great sight again. DR. ERICA (8) was game in defeat off the inside draw last start, finishing second and beaten one length (24.79) behind Astute Queen at this track. Has a strong record out of this box with five wins and three minor placings from 12 starts. Can feature again. STITCH AND SHOUT (6) found the frame here last start and looks a top-three hope again.",
